\c 138
\s Kuvonga kwomunhu anovimba
\s naJehovha
\s Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Ndichakuvongai nornwoyo wangu wose;
\s Ndichakuimbirai nziyo
\s dzokurumbidza
\s pamberi pavamwari.
\p
\v 2 Ndichanamata ndakatarira
\s kutemberi yenyu tsvene, Nokuvonga zita renyu nokuda kwounyoro hwenyu nokutendeka
\s kwenyu;
\s Nokuti makakurisa shoko renyu kupfuura zita renyu rose.
\p
\v 3 Pazuva randakadana makandipindura,
\s Makandisimbisa nesimba pamweya wangu.
\p
\v 4 Madzimambo ose enyika achakuvongai, Jehovha,
\s Nokuti vakanzwa mashoko omuromo wenyu.
\p
\v 5 Zvirokwazvo, vachaimba vachireva nzira dzaJehovha;
\s Nokuti kubwinya kwaJehovha kukuru.
\p
\v 6 Nokuti Jehovha ari kumusoro, kunyange zvakadaro ane hanya neanozvininipisa;
\s Asi anamanyawi Jehovha
\s anomuziva ari kure.
\p
\v 7 Kana ndichifamba pakati penhamo, imi muchandiponesa; Muchatambanudza ruoko rwenyu kudzivisa kutsamwa kwavavengi
\s vangu,
\s Ruoko rwenyu rworudyi ruchandiponesa.
\p
\v 8 Jehovha achandikwanisira zvinhu zvangu;
\s Ngoni dzenyu, Jehovha, dzinogara nokusingaperi;
\s Musarega mabasa amaoko enyu.
